          |  OpenAI Sora Technology Overview
        .card-body
          h5.card-subtitle.mb-3.text-muted A Glimpse into AI-Powered Video Creation
          p.
            OpenAI Sora leverages cutting-edge AI technology to transform text prompts into high-quality videos.
            Built on a diffusion transformer architecture, it iteratively refines noisy video inputs to produce
            coherent and visually stunning outputs. The system is trained on an extensive dataset, including publicly
            available and licensed video content, enabling it to generate a diverse range of creative scenes.
          ul.list-group.list-group-flush
            li.list-group-item
              i.bi.bi-diagram-3-fill
              |  Architecture: Denoising latent diffusion model powered by transformers.
            li.list-group-item
              i.bi.bi-collection-play-fill
              |  Capabilities: Generate videos up to 1080p, with creative tools like "Remix," "Loop," and "Blend."
            li.list-group-item
              i.bi.bi-boxes
              |  Training Data: Diverse dataset of publicly available and licensed videos.
            li.list-group-item
              i.bi.bi-exclamation-triangle-fill.text-warning
              |  Limitations: Challenges with complex physics, causality, and restrictions on realistic human depictions.
